<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>She recently announced she is pregnant with her second child to fiancé Matthew 'Matty J' Johnson.</p>

<p>And on Wednesday, Laura Byrne teased the name of their next baby during an interview with the Kyle and Jackie O show.</p>

<p>Host Kyle Sandilands asked: 'Will you be calling the new child also like a hillbilly female name as well? Are you doing the hyphenated thing?</p>

<p>'We're not going to disappoint': Pregnant Laura Byrne teased the name she and fiancé Matty J have chosen for their second child</p>

<p>The brunette beauty, who welcomed her first daughter Marlie-Mae in June 2019, said: 'We have an equally bogan name up our sleeves guys.'</p>

<p>'Don't worry, we're not going to disappoint,' she laughed.  </p>

<p>Last week, the couple hinted at the sex of their unborn baby, during an appearance on Studio 10.</p>

<p>Boy or girl? Last week, the couple hinted at the sex of their unborn baby, during an appearance on Studio 10 (pictured).</p>

<p>Matty guessed they were having a boy, but said he would be happy with either gender. </p>

<p>'I don't know if this is wishful thinking, but there's lots of kicks right now, so for me, I'm like alright we have a little soccer player, rugby player' he said. </p>

<p>Meanwhile, Laura stayed mum during the discussion, making sure not to reveal whether or not she knew what gender their soon-to-be bundle of joy was. </p>

<p>Another baby on the way! Matty and Laura announced they are expecting their second child together last Thursday. He joked on his Instagram post: 'Please brace yourself for twice the amount of dad jokes'</p>

<p>Matty and Laura announced they are expecting their second child together last Thursday.</p>

<p>'Marlie-Mae learning shocked face couldn't have been timed any better.. WE'RE HAVING A BABY!' Matty wrote alongside a family photo on Instagram.</p>

<p>'Please brace yourself for twice the amount of dad jokes,' he added.</p>

<p>Matty and Laura met and fell in love on The Bachelor three years ago. In April last year, the loved-up couple got engaged while on holiday in Fiji. </p>

